fr.smile.socialnetworking.service.persistence
Class MeetupsEntryUtil

java.lang.Object
  fr.smile.socialnetworking.service.persistence.MeetupsEntryUtil

public class MeetupsEntryUtil
extends Object

The persistence utility for the meetups entry service. This utility wraps MeetupsEntryPersistenceImpl and provides direct access to the database for CRUD operations. This utility should only be used by the service layer, as it must operate within a transaction. Never access this utility in a JSP, controller, model, or other front-end class.

Caching information and settings can be found in portal.properties

Author:
Brian Wing Shun Chan
See Also:
MeetupsEntryPersistence, MeetupsEntryPersistenceImpl
